  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db4\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 21 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "App fuel from 21",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa, President of the Petrol Station Owners Association, said today (18) morning that fuel will be released from next Thursday (21st) according to the 'National Fuel Licence' and Cipetco will not mind queuing up at petrol stations.",
        "From Thursday, Q.R. Mr. Kumara Rajapaksa said that fuel will be issued only according to the symbol and the registration number of the vehicle and also mentioned that the people who are currently in the queue should leave.",
        "Accordingly, Mr. Rajapaksa further said that only vehicle owners with the last digit of the vehicle registration number 0, 1 and 2 should come to get fuel on the 21st."
      ],
